    <title>DCLG business plan 2011 to 2015</title>
    <category>Publication</category>
    <summary>The Department for Communities and Local Government (DCLG) business plan sets out work DCLG plans to carry out between 2011 and 2015</summary>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;The DCLG business plan was published on 13 May 2011 as part of a co-ordinated relaunch of departmental business plans by Oliver Letwin, Minister of State at the Cabinet Office. It contains the changes DCLG have adopted following the consultation on the indicators and information strategy.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It also includes an update of the structural reform plan showing what actions have been complete to bring it into line with the latest information on the No 10 database. It also contains new actions to reflect new policies including the growth review and the social mobility white paper.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
